title: 1992–93 Croatian Football Cup
text:
The 1992–93 <a href="Croatian%20Football%20Cup">Croatian Football Cup</a> was the second season of <a href="Croatia">Croatia</a>'s <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> knockout competition. <a href="NK%20Inter%20Zapre%C5%A1i%C4%87">Inter Zaprešić</a> were the defending champions.
Semi-finals.
Second legs.
"Croatia Zagreb won 3–2 on aggregate."
"Hajduk Split won 4–2 on aggregate."
Final.
Second leg.
"Hajduk Split won 5–3 on aggregate."
